	Fix MDB_CURRENT (ITS#7793)
	Fix possible crash on Windows DLL detach
	Misc code cleanup
	Documentation
		mdb_cursor_put: cursor moves on error (ITS#7771)


LMDB 0.9.11 Release (2014/01/15)
