	Fix Windows/MSVC build issues
	Raise safe limit of max MDB_MAXKEYSIZE
	Misc code cleanup
	Documentation
		Remove spurious note about non-overlapping flags (ITS#7665)

LMDB 0.9.10 Release (2013/11/12)
